parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front end ball joints can cause the vehicle to wander or drift while driving, leading to loss of control and potential accidents. It can also lead to uneven tire wear, reducing the overall safety and performance of the vehicle.
symptoms: The vehicle wanders or drifts while driving
front end feels loose or unstable
ball joints pop out while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the door/alarm switches can cause the alarm to go off unnecessarily, leading to inconvenience and potential safety risks.
The failure of the seat belt can lead to serious injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The seat belt fails to operate during an accident
the seat belt does not restrain the occupant properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracking and disintegration of the dashboard can create a safety hazard by exposing electrical components, airbags, and other critical systems, potentially leading to electrical shorts, fires, or airbag malfunctions.
symptoms: The dashboard cracks and breaks into sharp pieces
chunks of the dashboard fall off

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Rust and Corrosion on Door Panels
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Rust and corrosion on the door panels can compromise the structural integrity of the doors, potentially leading to water intrusion, electrical system failures, and reduced safety in the event of a crash.
symptoms: Rust bubbles under the factory paint
rust and corrosion on the door frames.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine shaking, stalling, and transmission fluid leaks can cause loss of control, accidents, and difficulty maneuvering.
Steering gear box failure can cause loss of control, accidents, and difficulty maneuvering, especially on mountain roads.
symptoms: vehicle moves all over the road

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the hood latch can cause the hood to release while driving, obstructing the driver's view and potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: The hood of the vehicle releases while driving
the hood bends backwards and smashes into the windshield

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power door locks can cause the doors to automatically close or become stuck, creating a safety hazard in emergency situations where occupants need to exit the vehicle quickly.
symptoms: The doors automatically close or lock while driving
the doors cannot be opened manually or with the control
the doors can only be opened after repeated attempts.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can lead to the failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash, increasing the risk of injury or fatality to vehicle occupants.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates on the dashboard
indicating a malfunction within the system.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Failure of Airbags to Deploy in Crash
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in a crash can increase the risk of injury or fatality to vehicle occupants.
symptoms: Airbags fail to deploy in a head-on collision or other crash scenario
despite the severity of the impact.
